{"tid":152840,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"真係好想養寵物，歡迎各屆人士比建議","createTime":"2017-03-12T06:25:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-18T18:46:46.000Z","uid":55514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d79ccf68577de5d6b113708aa05ac1175661f468","tid":152840,"uid":55514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T06:25:49.000Z","msg":"我由細到大已經好中意動物，細過養左隻龜一路到依家，就放左係廳，另外仲有個魚缸着金魚(之前養過無數熱帶魚)<br />\n本身係房養緊兩巢蟻<br />\n近排，想係房養多隻寵物<br />\n貓狗一定唔得，屋企多擺設，驚啲貓會掃跌曬<br />\n龜同魚都唔係咁想<br />\n鼠就100%唔得，因為家母驚<br />\n雀都唔得<br />\n除以上外<br />\n巴打有冇其他建議?<br />\n有考慮過甲蟲同埋變色龍，但變色龍係咪要買好多設備?<br />\n同埋好似有隻6角龍幾易養(白身紅色六隻角)"},{"pid":"d2a1f799304719f60b5889085316fc45653517bc","tid":152840,"uid":20448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T06:27:29.000Z","msg":"蛇囉"},{"pid":"44814d0278f8c563b0e2eb338cba553f1d000d36","tid":152840,"uid":63515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T06:32:02.000Z","msg":"守宮 角蛙 變色龍"},{"pid":"2312066a21205bbcc98df63899edee53c313369b","tid":152840,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T06:33:23.000Z","msg":"甲蟲，要好比心機"},{"pid":"42e0fb277cb531f73a82d8110c8223959bdffca9","tid":152840,"uid":55514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T06:35:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蛇囉</blockquote><br />\n蛇應該都唔得，屋企人有偏見，但都好多謝巴打嘅意見，其實我都好想養球蟒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啱啱見到有個巴打嘅post好葡萄"},{"pid":"5199f0461a528f6cc2edcd18b92f50b95055996d","tid":152840,"uid":55514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T06:37:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>守宮 角蛙 變色龍</blockquote><br />\n如果要養守宮or變色龍，平民種+所有設備大約幾多?之前係魚街見到隻變色龍大約7-10cm長，400蚊一隻，但佢好得意，價錢都可以接受"},{"pid":"ee488773352a870769c47f2db6ebec12cd62ab72","tid":152840,"uid":55514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T06:40:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>甲蟲，要好比心機</blockquote><br />\n點解咁講?因為個結蛹孵化問題?<br />\n我諗住係養甲蟲的話，會養海克力斯或者長頸鹿"},{"pid":"903f0b375f8ceac8a3e673586a137784b9f218b5","tid":152840,"uid":58622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T06:43:12.000Z","msg":"甲蟲成蟲好易養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />l但由幼蟲養就要d技巧同耐性"},{"pid":"05bc2d5873123c6121a859d9f974da108fdc139d","tid":152840,"uid":55514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T06:53:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>甲蟲成蟲好易養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />l但由幼蟲養就要d技巧同耐性</blockquote><br />\n一定係由幼蟲養起，成功感大好多"},{"pid":"bf919c05bc180aa3ac9ebf5b73ea1170001a3874","tid":152840,"uid":82744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T06:58:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>守宮 角蛙 變色龍</blockquote><br />\n如果要養守宮or變色龍，平民種+所有設備大約幾多?之前係魚街見到隻變色龍大約7-10cm長，400蚊一隻，但佢好得意，價錢都可以接受</blockquote><br />\n守宮比起變色龍需要既設備少好多<br />\n一個膠缸，廚房紙做底材，水兜，洞穴(想平可以用膠花盆剪開一半)，冬天要暖墊，加加埋埋二百蚊有找"},{"pid":"656f37cf1f94826e2248c4c02680858462077acc","tid":152840,"uid":58622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T07:01:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>甲蟲成蟲好易養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />l但由幼蟲養就要d技巧同耐性</blockquote><br />\n一定係由幼蟲養起，成功感大好多</blockquote><br />\n都係嘅,咁仲易養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />養長㦸幼蟲基本上用一個大/加大缸養,然後每2個月換次泥就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />勁啱懶人養"},{"pid":"1b773b96903b5fff300b3fe31d24714e249da569","tid":152840,"uid":79278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T07:23:48.000Z","msg":"六角龍唔易養"},{"pid":"ddc540ba051ae11deafff0a59ca45f5e4ef26db8","tid":152840,"uid":26875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T07:25:14.000Z","msg":"刺蝟"},{"pid":"551dc9fd379374fcf6f624b5f612da374280bddf","tid":152840,"uid":55514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":