eplyTime":"2017-03-12T07:30:26.000Z","msg":"養緊貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 領養番黎<br />\n佢比以前個主人係垃圾房汁番黎"},{"pid":"2e51828a809e3906f7bd8219dd480202be4d189b","tid":152840,"uid":81956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T07:30:31.000Z","msg":"養曱甴 唔洗打理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9aec65796f89662b3101c12a861e04dd01eb0fb","tid":152840,"uid":55514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T07:31:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>甲蟲成蟲好易養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />l但由幼蟲養就要d技巧同耐性</blockquote><br />\n一定係由幼蟲養起，成功感大好多</blockquote><br />\n都係嘅,咁仲易養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />養長㦸幼蟲基本上用一個大/加大缸養,然後每2個月換次泥就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />勁啱懶人養</blockquote>咁有啲一罐，要放啲唔知咩菌果啲係for咩?</blockquote><br />\n鍬型蟲的幼蟲</blockquote><br />\n我上網睇下先，真係唔知，雖然我成日去蟲森<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"350e72c365652015722ac121e95a9b4e0d767982","tid":152840,"uid":7631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T07:31:37.000Z","msg":"牛"},{"pid":"9bb192a19f5c217de70780ddf48a24d0079af8ed","tid":152840,"uid":55514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T07:32:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>養緊貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 領養番黎<br />\n佢比以前個主人係垃圾房汁番黎</blockquote><br />\n我都想養呀:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我係貓奴，我都想要主子呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{